    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Those who march down the path of courage are exceptional with a blade, and you are no different. After casting this jutsu, when you take the attack action increase the number of attacks you can make with a weapon by +1. For every hit that lands with the attack action, increase your attack bonus by +1 until the end of the turn.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> For each rank you upcast this jutsu, increase the cost by 3. If upcast to C-Rank, if you hit with at least 2 attacks you can force the target creature to make a Strength saving throw, knocking them prone and back 15 feet on a failure.</p><p>If upcast to B-Rank, this jutsu gains the Combo keyword and you can target one affected creature with a Bukijutsu <em><strong>Finisher</strong></em> as a reaction, regardless of range, once per turn, ignoring its listed casting time. All boosts to attack and critical threat range from this jutsu apply to the Finisher cast.</p><p>If upcast to A-Rank, increase the number of attacks you make with the attack action by +1.</p><p>If upcast to S-Rank, for each attack you land with your weapon your critical threat range increases by +1 until the end of the turn.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
